se.miun.itm.input.model.mapping
Interface IMapping

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<IMapping>, Dependable<IMapping>, Identifiable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AMapping, EmptyMapping, Mapping
public interface IMapping
extends Identifiable, Dependable<IMapping>, java.lang.Comparable<IMapping>

A mapping represents a single InPUT mapping element within the code mapping tree. It is an extended pojo of the content in the mapping file, with easy access to class definitions.

Author:
Felix Dobslaw
